    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/d177ad1902ec638ea7ab0368ba7a4dfe.poster.avif?t=1698447464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/d177ad1902ec638ea7ab0368ba7a4dfe.webm?t=1698447464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/d177ad1902ec638ea7ab0368ba7a4dfe.mp4?t=1698447464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩宾果游戏：<br>宾果游戏是一款经典世代相传的游戏，我们为其注入了现代元素，让您千万不要错过！您可以同时使用两张或四张卡片进行游戏，选择男声或女声播报号码，并调整号码播报速度。多种技巧难度和无穷的娱乐机会，让您永远都不会厌倦大喊 &quot;宾果&quot;！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/738e950f85c0dc8109cd41a0a80fbdeb.poster.avif?t=1698447464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/738e950f85c0dc8109cd41a0a80fbdeb.webm?t=1698447464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/738e950f85c0dc8109cd41a0a80fbdeb.mp4?t=1698447464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为水獭建造温馨豪宅：<br>加入勤劳的水獭家族，为它们建造适合任何季节的舒适住所！用独特的家具和装饰品打造他们豪宅的每个角落，并观察水獭们享受自己的新家。无论您是室内设计爱好者，还是只想寻找乐趣，这款游戏都能让您笑容满面。<br><br>收集拼图：<br>在这个令人兴奋的宾果冒险游戏中，解决拼图并解锁新的涂鸦笔！每个关卡都有新的挑战等待着您，找寻难以捉摸的拼图碎片，拼凑出精美的图片。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/f56adc00e9bf46232729aa50e6ef8fec.poster.avif?t=1698447464\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367580/extras/f56adc00e9bf46232729aa50e6ef8fec.webm?t=169844